{"tid":860930,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該波台5大智將: 蓋ching 卡勞 2和B N賓 佩雷斯 入一入黎 講下10大填海方案邊個先係最好?","createTime":"2018-10-13T17:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T16:02:23.000Z","uid":44748,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"280711fb886536a4f989ce6c6fd53554f3cef33a","tid":860930,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"方案1: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cu9x7Xz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcu9x7Xz.png&h=cc1091f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n245公傾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方案2:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKDZNXD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzKDZNXD.png&h=0765ea55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n481公傾<br />\n<br />\n方案3:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Wc7WQ6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Wc7WQ6.png&h=e78ba5f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3615公傾<br />\n<br />\n方案4: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZxcowa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZxcowa.png&h=cd98bb54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n511公傾<br />\n<br />\n方案5:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8w1gRe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8w1gRe.png&h=b1d90474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n649公傾<br />\n<br />\n方案6:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dhBMsXX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhBMsXX.png&h=7a11fdc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n865公傾<br />\n<br />\n方案7:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jb9VkuY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjb9VkuY.png&h=d8b70c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n475公傾<br />\n<br />\n方案8:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fppNWRF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfppNWRF.png&h=ae22886b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n300公傾<br />\n<br />\n方案9:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0J3OGip.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0J3OGip.png&h=02d6bc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n745公傾<br />\n<br />\n方案10:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Qzx7Ys.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Qzx7Ys.png&h=53b67f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n473公傾<br />\n<br />\n另附填海解釋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/860211/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/860211/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n棕地 高爾夫球場收地收10年都收唔到 因為一牽涉法律政府係搞唔掂<br />\ncut150 又牽涉政治 又唔得<br />\ncut 郊野公園又牽涉政治 同法律 又唔得<br />\n<br />\n所以填海係唯一方法係短時間取得大量土地<br />\n<br />\n咁填邊到好? 高鐵去西九又唔係去大魚山 幫高鐵搶客幫助細<br />\n所以東大魚山係要填 但係填近岸500頃就夠 成本平好多<br />\n<br />\n所以建議填東大魚山果500 一樣叫明日之島 但係做大彎區商業一島 即係唔起公屋<br />\n咁咪配合到你想玩一帶一路既效果lo<br />\n<br />\n另外就填哂個吐露淘去到大尾篤 有2000頃 <br />\n起條新鐵路比果到 咩馬鞍山 科學園全部方便哂 搵唔到反對理由<br />\n呢到起Q哂D公屋 又解決到居住問題<br />\n<br />\n將商業同住宅區分拆 就可以減少貴價填海既壓力<br />\n成件事目的就係令到填海易左 成本低左<br />\n<br />\n沒錯呢個做法跟本做唔到大家想做到既野<br />\n<br />\n但係配合<br />\n1. 一帶一路既經濟發展 <br />\n2. 保存庫房 <br />\n3. 解決住居需要 <br />\n4. 解決多方面爭議<br />\n5. 短時間搞掂 迴避多方面法律問題 增加所有持分者利益<br />\n<br />\n諗唔到有咩可以反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本得個反字說服唔到政府做野<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>5 win situation都唔得?</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba92db2518d89107a880a13142c7161938829d2","tid":860930,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"任揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca40d4844ca87b7f2a53805634ffef1b7593a514","tid":860930,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T17:09:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84669da7701515ddc72a94d4a5518e2c488be207","tid":860930,"uid":38189,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8